    <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[ (\operatorname {Spec} f)^{-1}(O_a) = O_{fa} ]]></fr:tex>
    for any <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a \in  D]]></fr:tex>, hence this is a spectral map.
